It didn't really seem to
get me what I wanted to do.

00:19:10.830 --> 00:19:14.800
So I locked myself away for three
months in my office and wrote a new one.

00:19:14.800 --> 00:19:16.790
And they didn't meet our needs.

00:19:16.790 --> 00:19:17.800
That's why they weren't flexible.

