00:21:33.510 --> 00:21:36.510
I'm just going to talk about
the ARD stuff today though.

00:21:36.520 --> 00:21:37.600
Okay.

00:21:37.690 --> 00:21:40.810
So I didn't realize we were going
to see such extensive ARD stuff

00:21:40.870 --> 00:21:43.000
at the conference so I won't go
into this as much as I thought.

00:21:43.040 --> 00:21:44.600
But ARD is a killer product.

00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:46.960
It's got some seriously
powerful hardware searching.

00:21:46.990 --> 00:21:49.650
You can do some really nice
lab organization and imaging

00:21:49.710 --> 00:21:50.710
options with this stuff.

