We select the allocation of the lab,
so we say this machine is

00:33:20.090 --> 00:33:22.720
going to be a staff machine,
it's going to Green 14,

00:33:22.760 --> 00:33:25.500
it's going to be a
Final Cut machine in the purple lab.

00:33:25.570 --> 00:33:28.740
The machine net boots,
queries the help desk, says hello,

00:33:28.740 --> 00:33:30.260
I'm new here, what should I do?

00:33:30.330 --> 00:33:32.660
The help desk system says,
well you're in Green 13 my friend,

00:33:32.810 --> 00:33:35.430
I'd like you to boot from this server,
this is the software

00:33:35.430 --> 00:33:38.040
